## Features

✨ **Modern Stack**: Angular 21+ with SSR, Tailwind CSS 4+
🎨 **Themes**: Easy-to-customize theme system
🔌 **Plugins**: Extensible plugin architecture
📊 **SEO/AEO**: Built-in SEO optimization
🗄️ **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
⚡ **Fast**: Server-side rendering for optimal performance

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Set up database
pnpm db:setup

# Start development server
pnpm dev:ssr

# Open browser
open http://localhost:<%= port %>
```

## Admin Panel

Access the admin panel at: `http://localhost:<%= port %>/admin`

