## Customization

### Themes
Create custom themes in `src/themes/` - see existing themes for examples.

### Plugins
Build plugins in `src/plugins/` - check out the template and examples.

## Scripts

```bash
pnpm dev              # Development server (client-side)
pnpm dev:ssr          # Development server (SSR)
pnpm build            # Production build
pnpm build:ssr        # Production build with SSR
pnpm serve:ssr        # Serve production build

pnpm prisma:generate  # Generate Prisma client
pnpm prisma:migrate   # Run database migrations
pnpm prisma:seed      # Seed database
pnpm prisma:studio    # Open Prisma Studio
pnpm db:setup         # Complete database setup
```

